{"tid":1369483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果元朗再請外判......","createTime":"2019-07-26T17:00:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T03:31:56.000Z","uid":51818,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"49e6ebc4a4b145e817520245bd7df5b1f31f8530","tid":1369483,"uid":51818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:00:45.000Z","msg":"大家好，我今次出Post唔係要講啲咩，是純粹想分享俾大家聽我發咗個夢。<br />\n<br />\n好多手足都話唔好入村，唔好搞墳場同祠堂，亦都唔好衝鄉事大樓。呢三點我都好認同，因為經歷過７２１元朗事件，有好多深藍開始倒戈向淺藍，又或者淺黃。如果我地衝入去，啲藍屍又會覺得我地喺到倒亂，民意亦會逆轉，所以我地都要保持冷靜。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然，如果一個平民百姓入元朗行個街，食個Ｂ仔，做下文青影相，都無端端俾啲唔識嘅人嘅時候，我地梗係要還手啦！<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">手足還手係自衛，而唔係暴徒搞事！</span></strong></span>身邊嘅人幫手拍低之餘，都要打俾９９９。雖然，警察唔一定可以喺１５分鐘內到，又唔一定會帶齊裝備，但都照報警。因為<strong><ins>警察係唔會遲多過八個字到，佢地只會遲３９分鐘。</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VF5q4Hp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVF5q4Hp.jpg&h=8c3ba46f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同場加映 : 自衛術教學<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ohpama.com/442709/24parent/%E6%AD%A6%E8%A1%93%E6%95%99%E7%B7%B44%E6%8B%9B%E8%87%AA%E8%A1%9B%E8%A1%93-%E9%98%B2%E8%97%A4%E6%A2%9D%E8%A5%B2%E6%93%8A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohpama.com%2F442709%2F24parent%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E8%25A1%2593%25E6%2595%2599%25E7%25B7%25B44%25E6%258B%259B%25E8%2587%25AA%25E8%25A1%259B%25E8%25A1%2593-%25E9%2598%25B2%25E8%2597%25A4%25E6%25A2%259D%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E6%2593%258A%2F&d=vhywW4AIbf33TEOu71%2FwUz11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=9a32678c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ohpama.com/442709/24parent/%E6%AD%A6%E8%A1%93%E6%95%99%E7%B7%B44%E6%8B%9B%E8%87%AA%E8%A1%9B%E8%A1%93-%E9%98%B2%E8%97%A4%E6%A2%9D%E8%A5%B2%E6%93%8A/</a><br />\n<br />\n而我最想最想講嘅係，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">「入村」呢個詞語真係好詭異，好伏！</span></span></strong>元朗十八鄉主席今日「溫馨提示」示威者唔好越過村界，否則村民會有所行動。但係，其實<strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">元朗好多地方係暫未劃定村界</span></span></strong>，咁即係村長話邊度係村界就係村界。佢一聲下令話要打人，白衣人就可以又再出動打人。<br />\n<br />\n附上立場新聞一則 : <strong><em>往元朗示威者注意　隨時入咗村都唔知</em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%BE%80%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F-%E9%9A%A8%E6%99%82%E5%85%A5%E5%92%97%E6%9D%91%E9%83%BD%E5%94%94%E7%9F%A5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25BE%2580%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%25B3%25A8%25E6%2584%258F-%25E9%259A%25A8%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%2592%2597%25E6%259D%2591%25E9%2583%25BD%25E5%2594%2594%25E7%259F%25A5%2F&d=vhywW4AIbf33TEOu71%2FwUz11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=6c160034\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25BE%2580%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%25B3%25A8%25E6%2584%258F-%25E9%259A%25A8%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%2592%2597%25E6%259D%2591%25E9%2583%25BD%25E5%2594%2594%25E7%259F%25A5%2F&h=018d2e0f\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%BE%80%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F-%E9%9A%A8%E6%99%82%E5%85%A5%E5%92%97%E6%9D%91%E9%83%BD%E5%94%94%E7%9F%A5/</a><br />\n<br />\n但係，最奇怪嘅係，<strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">我覺得今次佢地已經唔會再搵白衣人</span></strong>，呢啲低Lv.嘅雜兵出嚟。反而，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我發夢記得佢地好似話會再請出面啲人返嚟，我真係發夢聽到架，</strong></span></span>佢地話要招呼遠道而來嘅訪客，我諗大家都好清楚我講緊咩。<br />\n<br />\n我發呢個夢，係希望各位手足萬事小心，唔好跌落敵人嘅陷阱。另外，自己都評估一下聽日瞓晏教，去發夢嘅風險。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">不流血　不受傷　不被捕　<br />\n不分化　不篤灰　不割席</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U1KjpNG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU1KjpNG.png&h=61af6627&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2031070482c7c5e8072e60efef0f9ac5f1136535","tid":1369483,"uid":276208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:01:51.000Z","msg":"借位一用<br />\n<br />\n<strong>請幫推到鄉民見到，希望聽日可以相安無事</strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">誠懇請鄉民今次真係要<ins>阻止任何可疑人士（包括疑似示威者）入村</ins>，唔係又引起誤會／衝突就唔好啦~~ </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n[投訴懶人包] 反對套丁及冒充原居民 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1369127\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1369127</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: blue;\">齊上齊落，支持五大訴求<br />\n支持圍村去黑，還我平靜鄉郊<br />\n反恐反黑，由投訴撚做起</span></em>"},{"pid":"edcb5da6e109f078bdc250f615f1ed2642dd9057","tid":1369483,"uid":128850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:01:58.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"2b344832f4db32d770f1b79b17e60935d7e16f30","tid":1369483,"uid":51818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:12:26.000Z","msg":"同埋，都知道有啲手足對元朗呢知地方有啲陌生，但又會想去元朗一日遊。所以都搵咗啲地方俾大家去、，希望大家玩得開心。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gFyj9kh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgFyj9kh.jpg&h=e380a71b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y1jjpTD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy1jjpTD.jpg&h=cf56df57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q7yoRyD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq7yoRyD.jpg&h=6e2d3beb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zRZrPkj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzRZrPkj.jpg&h=523b2321&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FkyXbyE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFkyXbyE.jpg&h=960e872c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aBdL4TF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaBdL4TF.jpg&h=cfefdb6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b9sUdM2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb9sUdM2.jpg&h=d2e52ea3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"781273c4c07af2703a0ce9a9e38e9d354f291b0f","tid":1369483,"uid":128850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:14:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a1822a77736674151e05399bc950cbf4abe90237","tid":1369483,"uid":128850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:14:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0401d1a4d0380447f8a36031eb38ebaccc68b982","tid":1369483,"uid":51818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:23:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f34f0f19099be18d56a63d690334280e1e5bb68d","tid":1369483,"uid":9315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:24:22.000Z","msg":"唔好expect call黑警救到你  唔打柒你都偷笑"},{"pid":"80bd3ebbdac2571cf1c6957988e895ebbf6cdf42","tid":1369483,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f34f0f19099be18d56a63d690334280e1e5bb68d","tid":1369483,"uid":9315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:24:22.000Z","msg":"唔好expect call黑警救到你  唔打柒你都偷笑"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:25:42.000Z","msg":"班黑社會小人, 就即刻出黎<br />\n班黑社會人多, 就成班黑警唔見晒<br />\n<br />\n警黑合作"},{"pid":"1f1444b866770c11888b93f9d07364917c6e6ea9","tid":1369483,"uid":271051,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:25:54.000Z","msg":"一定要自衛"},{"pid":"00db2160b259fbefca760b393fda58af2268e449","tid":1369483,"uid":9315,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:25:59.000Z","msg":"被鄉黑打個陣call黑警只會有兩種結果<br />\n1. 唔應  (說明鄉黑佔優  你仆街啦)<br />\n2. 出黎拉鳩你 (唔好FF係應你call 實情係鄉黑唔夠抽call左馬)"},{"pid":"b20128243d690c024b01c6d56cb08208030abf79","tid":1369483,"uid":9315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80bd3ebbdac2571cf1c6957988e895ebbf6cdf42","tid":1369483,"uid